article_id:3048,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia started on <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>■What Are Gala Dragalia and Gala Dragalia Remix?</div><div>The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons is boosted to 6%, which is up from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">The newly added 5★ adventurer Gala Nedrick and 5★ dragon Primal Brunhilda will also appear in a Gala Dragalia available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1649224799"></span>, but they will not be featured in that showcase. Primal Brunhilda will also appear in subsequent summon showcases.</span></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">The Scratch-A-Thon Summon that is live at the same time does not include the newly added featured adventurers or dragons appearing in this showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>▼Newly added featured adventurer:</div><div>5★ Gala Nedrick (shadow/sword)</div><div><br></div><div>▼Newly added featured dragon:</div><div>5★ Primal Brunhilda (flame)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 1.30% (Adventurers: 0.50%, Dragons: 0.80%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 4.70% (Adventurers: 2.50%, Dragons: 2.20%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%, Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Wyrmsigils may only be redeemed in the summon showcase from which they were earned. Wyrmsigils earned from this Gala Dragalia summon showcase cannot be redeemed in the Gala Dragalia available from <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1649224799"></span>.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia event duration:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648360800"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1648706399"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the featured adventurer and dragon below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured adventurer:</div><div>
