				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>The true seventh scion of Alberia. He was<br>afflicted with Wyrmscale shortly after birth and<br>taken to the Faerie Kingdom, where Bahamut<br>granted him a new chance at life. Pragmatic<br>and impersonal, he acts by his ideas alone.</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div><div class="skill explanation">
