						<li>The Flamewyrm Brunhilda with her regained<br>primal powers. Cloaked in brilliant flame, she is<br>fire incarnate, and burns all who oppose her to<br>ash. Her passion burns stronger still as she<br>stands by her beloved on the battlefield.</li>
